TRANSFER SOME OF THIS LOVE

19:28.501 --> 19:30.333
TO SOMEONE ELSE?
LIKE A COCKER SPANIEL?

19:30.419 --> 19:32.797
NOT A CHANCE.
SHE'S YOURS.

19:32.880 --> 19:35.247
SHE'S SO NICE TO ME.
SHE'S SO VERY GOOD.

19:35.299 --> 19:36.710
I KNOW.

19:36.801 --> 19:38.667
THE GLOVE CLEANER
IS THE ONLY WAY.

19:38.761 --> 19:41.093
WELL, I CAN'T DO THAT.

19:46.977 --> 19:51.517
UH, THERE MUST
BE ANOTHER WAY.

19:51.607 --> 19:53.689
THIS IS THE WAY.

19:53.776 --> 19:55.608
THE ONLY WAY.

19:55.695 --> 19:57.026
$1,000.

19:57.113 --> 19:58.478
