ALL MY SAVINGS!

20:11.335 --> 20:15.545
I KNOW. IT'S
ALWAYS THAT WAY.

20:15.631 --> 20:17.713
NO TRACE, NO ODOR,
NO TASTE.

20:17.800 --> 20:22.044
NO WAY TO DETECT.

20:22.138 --> 20:27.508
ALL RIGHT.

20:27.601 --> 20:29.888
AH, ALL
MADE OUT, EH?

20:29.979 --> 20:31.845
